    <li><strong>Complete Transaction Records</strong>: Every purchase with date, time, store, and items</li>
    <li><strong>Price History</strong>: Track price changes for products over time</li>
    <li><strong>Purchase Frequency</strong>: See how often you buy specific items</li>
    <li><strong>Store Patterns</strong>: Understand your shopping location preferences</li>
    <li><strong>Seasonal Trends</strong>: Identify seasonal purchasing patterns</li>
  </ul>

  <InfoBox type="success" title="Data Retention">
    Shopis stores your purchase history indefinitely with premium accounts, and up to 2 years with free accounts. All data is encrypted and securely backed up.
  </InfoBox>

