  <h2 id="receipt-management">Receipt Management</h2>
  <p>
    Keep all your receipts organized and easily accessible:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Digital Receipt Storage</strong>: Scan and store paper receipts</li>
    <li><strong>Email Receipt Import</strong>: Automatically import email receipts</li>
    <li><strong>OCR Technology</strong>: Extract data from receipt images automatically</li>
    <li><strong>Receipt Matching</strong>: Link receipts to purchase records</li>
    <li><strong>Tax Category Tagging</strong>: Mark receipts for tax deduction purposes</li>
  </ul>

  <InfoBox type="info" title="Receipt Processing">
    Shopis's OCR technology can extract data from 94% of receipts automatically, saving you time on manual data entry.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="reorder-features">Reorder Features</h2>
